      <title>OnAir 3.0.8</title>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 12:06:12 -0400</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>11</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.0.8</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>What's New in OnAir 3.0.8</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Fixed web meetings (Google Meet, Zoom Web, etc.) ending prematurely after 10 seconds.</li>
          <li>Shortcut confirmation window now appears in dark mode for a cleaner look.</li>
          <li>Shortcut confirmation avoids overlapping macOS Focus Mode notifications.</li>
          <li>Improved login items setup screen with new design and icon.</li>
          <li>Added Brave Browser support for web meeting detection.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
